              another gold token and not a fifth regional hub; it is the first
              unified global gold market — structurally larger than any single
              venue, and positioned to exceed any two major regional hubs
              combined.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>A clean wedge into stranded supply.</strong> 40–80
              institutional-grade allocated-custody vaults worldwide sit outside
              every incumbent hub, with no clearing pathway at all (Global Gold
              Research Census, May 2026 — 66 named facilities across 13
