            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            <strong>Governance.</strong> The Global Gold Council (Wyoming DUNA,
            Wyo. Stat. § 17-32) governs the protocol, with 2,045 on-chain members
            already constituting its statutory membership — distribution that
            exists before the raise, not after it. The OpCo board at seed is the
