          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 12 · THE ROUND -->
        <section id="round" class="memo-section" data-memo-section>
          <h2 class="display display--md">X. The Round</h2>
          <p>
            $5M priced Series Seed at $50M post: 1x non-participating preference,
            a 10% option pool from pre-money, a founder-designated board of two,
            founder-held super-voting common stock carrying 15–20 votes per share,
            and a Treasury Policy covenant that makes the gold-treasury discipline
